INSERT INTO testimonials (clientName, clientTitle, rating, testimonialText, serviceUsed, featured, approved, createdAt)
VALUES
('Michael Goldenberg', NULL, 5, 'I knew I was way off the mark with my current Resume, now very pleased with the updated version from Sonia. Communication was excellent with updating details and the whole experience was very simple and taken care of professionally. Thoroughly recommend going through the process to ensure being up to date, and now there is further room to improve prospects with the additional services. Thank you so much Sonia & Team @ All Resume Services.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('Megan Dawson', NULL, 5, 'As for my new resume and cover letter, I couldn''t be happier. After years of using the same old resume and constantly adding to it, it was looking pretty ordinary. I wasn''t overly keen to spend money on a new one, but I''m happy I did. The layout was nice, not overdone, the information came out good once our emailing sessions had finished, and the cover letter was very well worded. Also, the added bonus of the 22 attached documents regarding interview tips and techniques was excellent. I have, and will recommend your business to the hundreds of colleagues I have and wish you success for the future. Keep up the good work.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('B. Emard', NULL, 5, 'I reached out to Sonia and the team at All Resume Services a couple of years ago to have my resume and cover letter done upon moving to Australia. The service was extremely professional and prompt. I have had a lot of positive responses. -A year Ago', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('C. Brekke', NULL, 5, 'So I was like, in the market for a new job, ya know, and I stumbled upon All Resume Services (allresumeservices.com.au) so I gave it a go! Let me tell ya, Sonia was super quick in hooking me up with a new and improved resume, cover letter and selection criteria. I didn''t even realize how dated and wordy my old resume was until I got the shiny new one! The cover letter she made for me was super on point and legit, and guess what? It scored me an interview! I was SO close to landing that gig, but unfortunately, my location was just not right for them. But hey, at least I got to show off my shiny new resume and cover letter, right? Not only did Sonia give me some killer advice for the interview itself, but the final documentation she sent me with tips and tricks was super helpful for future interviews and job hunts. I highly recommend All Resume Services if you''re looking for professional and quick turnaround. Sonia is the bomb dot com! Thanks a bunch, girl!', NULL, 1, 1, NOW()),
('Shyam', NULL, 5, 'I have used All Resume Services for the first time about 5 years ago, the service I received it was excellent! Very professional service! within one week I scored an interview and was hired in two weeks! Recently I have changed careers I needed to update my Resume and cover letter. Sonia and the team come to mind! I contacted Sonia, within no time I had a brand new resume and cover letter, it was amazing! professionally done! I have alway found Sonia and the team to be very knowledgable in their field and believe me they know their stuff, you wont be disappointed. I will continue to use All Resume Services and recommend them to family, friends any one who needs help with a great professional resume service. Thank you Sonia and the Team.', NULL, 1, 1, NOW());
